title: Big Dickhead Energy with Luke Fracher
description:
Skkkkrrrrrr! Pull up to the LV trap house with a trunk full of your finest wears because this week the boys are dialing in the co-owner of Round Two, the legendary Luke Fracher aka OG Luke Mook. We’ve finally got Luke on the pod, slanging knowledge about how the game done changed, the craziest shit he’s ever copped at the shop, NYC vs. LA style, his favorite celebrity clientele, grails, the post-sneaker world, his new brand, managing a fleet of whips, defusing nuclear DMs, thirst trapping 101 and much more on this extremely legit and not fake episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
